{"tid":1526504,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:51:11.000Z","uid":266997,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9612d303df76d1650ef616a573dfc174c604a7e5","tid":1526504,"uid":266997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!<br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!"},{"pid":"b3f2e97b40472b2e4fc185a24fcdb4047dd98274","tid":1526504,"uid":1945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hO54gA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhO54gA1.jpg&h=d74b437d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/738QWA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F738QWA1.jpg&h=514540c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34WZPV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34WZPV2.jpg&h=e88f8e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41gCBA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41gCBA2.jpg&h=ba05256d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b41c388447d0d2afa7278cd03f1461fc65567ea","tid":1526504,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a747ab6670f4d441f84ea64a91ad21cc5ea9ab8","tid":1526504,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:25:48.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 